HEADWORD: Tagsore
<hw>Tag"sore`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Far.)</fld>
<def>Adhesion of the tail of a sheep to the wool from excoriation
produced by contact with the feces; -- called also
<altname>tagbelt</altname>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tagtail</ent>⟦br⟧
